                    "value": "The ASR Federal penlight comes with a super-bright white LED bulb that is great for law enforcement officers, nurses, and medical staff. You can use it as a pupil gauge while out in the field or examining patients. This portable penlight flashlight is convenient to use - it features a push-on/off button and will fit in just about any uniform pocket, duty belt or shirt pocket.<br/><br/>The flashlight pen measures just 5.5\" in length and weighs only .05 pounds (.8 ounces) so it won't add any bulk to your uniform or work clothes. The pen body is made of durable aluminum that won't rust or scratch, and it is powered by 2 AAA batteries (included). This is a great gift idea for nurses, medical staff, and law enforcement officers.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
